data.title: 1968 Press Photo Hermione Gingold English Film & Television Actress - RSC05157
data.meta_description: Historic Images Part Number: RSC05157. This is an original press photo. Hermione Gingold, English actress. Hermione Gingold (9 December 1897 - 24 May 1987) (pronounced with a hard "G", not as"Jinggold") was an English actress known for her sharp-tongued, eccentric persona, an image enhanced by her sharp nose and chin, as well as her deepening voice, a result of vocal nodes which her mother reportedly encouraged her not to remove.
